Layered Oil Painting Process]\n*[https://www.20minutos.es/noticia/2377973/0/christian-van-minnen/pintura/belleza-repulsiva/ Helena Celdr\u00e1n, \u201cChristian van Minnen: retratos y bodegones de belleza repulsiva,\u201d]\n\n2014 \n*\u201cCHRISTIAN REX VAN MINNEN INSTALLS GIANT BILLBOARD IN NY FOR THE ARTHA PROJECT,\u201d Upper Playground, November 22\n*[http://thewildmagazine.com/blog/rude-boys-christian-rex-van-minnen/ Marco Annunziata and Kate Messinger, \u201cRUDE BOYS: Christian Rex van Minnen,\u201d The Wild Magazine]\n\n2013 \n*Meghan MacRae, \u201cFever Dream...Christian Rex van Minnen,\u201d CVLT NATION, May 27\n*[http://www.beautifuldecay.com/2013/03/27/made-with-color-presents-the-grotesque-paintings-of-christian-rex-van-minnen/ Russ Crest, \u201cMade With Color Presents: The Grotesque Paintings Of Christian Rex van Minnen,\u201d Beautiful/Decay]\n*[http://animalnewyork.com/2013/artists-notebook-christian-rex-van-minnen/ Marina Galperina, \u201cArtist\u2019s Notebook: Christian Rex van Minnen,\u201d Animal, March 25]\n\n2010\n*Direct Art Magazine<ref name=\"Direct Art Magazine17\">{{cite journal |journal=Direct Art Magazine|title=full page |date=2010 |volume=17 |page=96}}</ref>\n\n2008 \n*[https://myloveforyou.typepad.com/my_love_for_you/2008/11/qa-with-christi.html Meighan O\u2019Toole, \u201cQ&A WITH CHRISTIAN REX VAN MINNEN,\u201d My Love for You Blog]\n\n==Radio, television, and film==\n\n*2015 Featured in @Large: Creators at Work TV Documentary Series, Redbull Production Studios, NYC<ref name=\"at large\">{{cite web |title=Diplo Presents: @LARGE \u2013 CREATORS AT WORK, New Series Produced by CRUSH+LAB and Red Bull Media House |url=http://www.raconteur.la/3721/diplo-presents-large-creators-at-work-inspiring-new-series-produced-by-crushlab-and-red-bull-media-house/ |website=raconteur |access-date=March 9, 2019 |date=2015-04-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170606041437/http://www.raconteur.la/3721/diplo-presents-large-creators-at-work-in