cBride, Mia Tyler\"\n|-\n| 2012\n| ''[[Adventure Time]]''\n| Farmworld [[Finn the Human|Finn]]'s mom (voice)\n| 2 episodes\n|-\n| 2013\n| ''[[Nashville (2012 TV series)|Nashville]]''\n| Calista Reeves\n| Episode: \"[[Nashville (season 1)#ep11|You Win Again]]\"\n|-\n| 2013\u2013present\n| ''[[Agents of S.H.I.E.L.D.]]''\n| Agent [[Melinda May]]\n| 116 episodes\n|-\n| 2014\n| ''[[Sofia the First]]''\n| [[Mulan (Disney character)|Fa Mula]]n (voice)\n| Episode: \"Princesses to the Rescue\"\n|-\n| 2017\u20132018\n| ''[[Milo Murphy's Law]]''\n| Savannah (voice)\n| 7 episodes\n|-\n| 2017\n| ''[[Fresh Off the Boat]]''\n| Stephanie\n| Episode: \"The Flush\"\n|-\n| 2017\u20132018\n| ''[[Sofia the First]]''\n| Vega (voice)\n| 5 episodes\n|-\n| 2017\n| ''[[We Bare Bears]]''\n| Ranger Zhao (voice)\n| Episode: \"Ranger Games\"\n|-\n| rowspan=\"2\" | 2018\n| ''[[Guardians of the Galaxy (TV series)|Guardians of the Galaxy]]''\n| [[Phyla-Vell|Phyla the Accuser]] (voice)\n| 4 episodes\n|-\n| ''[[Marvel Rising: Secret Warriors]]''\n| [[Hala the Accuser]] (voice)\n| Animated TV short film\n|-\n| 2018\u20132019\n| ''[[Hot Streets (TV series)|Hot Streets]]''\n| Soo Park (voice)\n| 6 episodes\n|-\n| 2018\u20132019\n| ''[[Fresh Off the Boat]]''\n| Elaine\n| 2 episodes\n|-\n| rowspan=\"3\" | 2019\n| ''[[Marvel Rising#Specials|Marvel Rising: Heart of Iron]]''\n| [[Hala the Accuser]] (voice)\n| Animated TV short film\n|-\n| ''[[Mao Mao: Heroes of Pure Heart]]''\n| Tanya Keys (voice)\n| Episode: \"Meet Tanya Keys\"\n|-\n| ''[[The Mandalorian]]''\n| [[Fennec Shand]]<ref name=\"Fennec\">{{cite web|last=Breznican|first=Anthony |title=First Look: Ming-Na Wen\u2019s Star Wars Assassin From The Mandalorian |url=https://www.vanityfair.com/hollywood/2019/11/ming-na-wen-the-mandalorian-star-wars-fennec-shand|website=Vanity Fair|date=November 4, 2019}}</ref>\n| Episode: \"[[Chapter 5: The Gunslinger|The Gunslinger]]\"\n|-\n| 2020\n| ''[[Awkwafina Is Nora from Queens]]''\n| Sandra\n| 2 episodes\n|-\n| 2020\n| ''[[Transformers: Siege]]''\n|\n| Upcoming series\n|-\n|}\n\n===Web series===\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\"\n! Year\n! Title\n! Role\n! class=\"unsortable\" | Notes\n|-\n| 2015\n| ''Parallel Man: Infinite Pursuit''\n| Major Mackenzie Cartwright\n| Voice\n|-\n| 2016\n| ''[[Agents of S.H.I.E.L.D.: Slingshot]]''\n| Agent Melinda May\n|-\n| 2020\n| ''[[List of original programs distributed by Quibi#Upcoming original programming|50 States of Fright]]''\n| TBA <ref>{{cite web|last1=Donnelly|first1=Matt|title=Jeffrey Katzenberg's Mobile Content Platform Orders Series From Jason Blum, Guillermo del Toro|url=https://variety.com/2018/biz/news/jeffrey-katzenbergs-wndrco-orders-series-from-jason-blum-guillermo-del-toro-1202975458|website=[[Variety (magazine)|Variety]]|accessdate=June 21, 2019|date=October 10, 2018}}</ref><ref name=\"April/Film\">{{cite web |last1=Pearson |first1=Ben |title=Everything Coming to Quibi in April, Including \u201950 States of Fright\u2019, \u2018Dishmantled\u2019, and Much More |url=https://www.slashfilm.com/everything-coming-to-quibi-in-april-2020/ |website=[[/Film]] |date=March 27, 2020}}</ref>\n| 3 episodes\n|}\n\n===Video games===\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\"\n! Year\n! Title\n! Role\n! class=\"unsortable\" | Notes\n|-\n| 1995\n| ''[[Street Fighter: The Movie (home video game)|Street Fighter: The Movie]]''\n| [[Chun-Li]]\n| rowspan=\"7\" |Voice\n|-\n| 1999\n| ''Disney's Story Studio: Mulan''\n| rowspan=\"4\" | [[Mulan (Disney character)|Fa Mulan]]\n|-\n| 2005\n| ''Disney's Story Studio: Mulan II''\n|-\n| 2006\n| ''[[Kingdom Hearts II]]''\n|-\n| 2015 \n| ''[[Disney Infinity 3.0]]''\n|-\n| rowspan=2 | 2016 \n| ''[[Lego Marvel's Avengers]]''\n| Agent Melinda May\n|-\n| ''Disney Magic Kingdoms''\n| Fa Mulan\n|}\n\n==Awards and nominations==\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n|- style=\"text-align:center;\"\n!style=\"background:#B0C4DE\"|Year\n!style=\"background:#B0C4DE\"|Award\n!style=\"background:#B0C4DE\"|Category\n!style=\"background:#B0C4DE\"